<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Indexed Chart Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Indexed charts can be created by setting the <Run FontWeight="Bold" xml:space="preserve">IsIndexed</Run> property of the chart series to <Run FontStyle="Italic">True</Run>. When a chart series is set to be indexed, the x values are treated as categories rather than values. All the points are simply plotted at an equal x distance, irrespective of the actual x value of the points.</Paragraph>

