Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem><Paragraph>Chart series data points can be indexed using the <Bold>IsIndexed</Bold> property.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Indexed"</Bold> will enable setting the <Bold>IsIndexed</Bold> property of the chart series to <Italic>True</Italic> or <Italic>False</Italic>. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The slider <Bold>"Chart Axis Interval"</Bold> will help in setting the x-axis interval. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>


</List>
